latestPosts.caption:
Latest cover shoot for @vogueindia ❤️

Posted @withregram • @vogueindia Through stories of victory laps and the daily grind, veterans Madhu Sapre (@sapremadhu) and Mehr Jesia (@mehrjesia) and vanguards Nayonikaa Shetty (@nayonikaashetty) and Anugraha Natarajan (@anugrahanatarajan) find a wonderful new kinship. Following the theme for Vogue India’s January-February 2024 issue, the sisters-in-arms compare chapters from their lives that underscore the strength of female friendships.

Tap the link in bio to read the full story.

Photographed by: Bikramjit Bose (@thebadlydrawnboy)
Styled by: James Lalthanzuala (@jameslalthanzuala)
Words by: Bandana Tewari (@behavebandana)
Hair & make-up artist: Mitesh Rajani (@miteshrajani)
Fashion assistants: Tarun Panwar (@taruntaruntarun), Amogha Salike (@amoghasalike), Sailee Inglee (@sailee.ingle).

From left, on Nayonikaa Shetty: Dress, Balenciaga (@balenciaga). Shoes, Christian Louboutin (@louboutinworld). On Madhu Sapre: Top, Pankaj & Nidhi (@pankajandnidhi). Jacket, Skirt; both Balenciaga (@balenciaga). Shoes, Christian Louboutin (@louboutinworld). On Anugraha Natarajan: Top, pants; both Pankaj & Nidhi (@pankajandnidhi). Shoes, Christian Louboutin (@louboutinworld). On Mehr Jesia: Dress, Amit Aggarwal (@amitaggarwalofficial). Shoes, Christian Louboutin @louboutinworld).
